{"tid":840474,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"忽發奇想，有冇人覺得龍心有生命危險","createTime":"2018-09-28T19:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T00:33:21.000Z","uid":20544,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"723b3121f890399eab70312fb74050032eebb3d0","tid":840474,"uid":20544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T19:39:10.000Z","msg":"相信大家都見到最近龍心啲po上哂熱門<br />\n又話山祝吹醒咗佢<br />\n仲有多個癲婆女朋友-女大j <br />\n雖然大家都瘋狂恥笑龍心<br />\n但大家有冇發現<br />\n龍心啲片嘅目的係乜？<br />\n「挑戰幣少」，「去外國人到挑機」，「揾地產佬招兵買馬」，「人地talk show搞事」⋯⋯<br />\n一連串嘅行為<br />\n都係證明自己比人地有料<br />\n又去考保險，地產牌<br />\n<br />\n但奇就奇在<br />\n佢之前先話龍心已死<br />\n王小虎誕生-一個追求社會公義，平淡過人生<br />\n又點會周圍搞搞陣？<br />\n就算之前men club訪問佢溝鬼妹<br />\n都係正正常常<br />\n點解一，兩個禮拜就變到神神化化？<br />\n<br />\n其實好多巴打都有討論過<br />\n就係因為佢辣著個癲婆<br />\n有留意龍心啲片<br />\n都會見到條女係咁讚龍心，例：<br />\nThe powerful man,無所不能，大愛，神⋯⋯<br />\n亦都係不斷重複呢幾句<br />\n對住龍心，佢就好似隻温柔小貓<br />\n但對住其他人，佢就即刻人格轉換，爆哂粗<br />\n我唔知道龍心有咩手段令到條女好似中咗降頭<br />\n但我淨係知道<br />\n如果龍心唔能夠再飾演條女心目中嘅神<br />\n咁佢嘅下場應該都幾恐怖下<br />\n<br />\n所以龍心不斷吹雞<br />\n又整哂ppt想sell自己<br />\n又話想開公司<br />\n究竟佢真係雄心壯志？<br />\n定係唯勢所逼？<br />\n<br />\n希望佢能安然度過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06de3e16bbb5c233d6476188d2e4ce7c139b23f3","tid":840474,"uid":8318,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T19:43:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> <span style=\"color: red;\">閲</span></span>"},{"pid":"63b9dbf70935946c59827d790d883afef2418abd","tid":840474,"uid":205530,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T20:00:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb290eee364a69d9aaa928a15081208aa21d921a","tid":840474,"uid":144264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T20:08:06.000Z","msg":"尋晚仲見佢係奧海城搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b7c4d556379a4849fdc0e103013a25ad089cb5","tid":840474,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T20:10:01.000Z","msg":"女fans病嬌 一物治一物"},{"pid":"916a0b3f9a173484ffbb5059041750925a6c87b2","tid":840474,"uid":20544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"63b9dbf70935946c59827d790d883afef2418abd","tid":840474,"uid":205530,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T20:00:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T20:12:45.000Z","msg":"如果我係佢就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又有樓<br />\n又食咁多女<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我唔會惹個癲婆先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90847758719c7a10c41e7eb08669a9d2bbf2e0fc","tid":840474,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T00:33:21.000Z","msg":"樓主係龍心條精蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}